camera3D.generators

Class SplitFrameGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • camera3D.generators.Generator
      • camera3D.generators.StereoscopicGenerator
        • camera3D.generators.SplitFrameGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    processing.core.PConstants

    public class SplitFrameGenerator
extends StereoscopicGenerator
    Split frame generator. This will pack the right and left component images into one composite image. The two components will be positioned vertically or horizontally. Also, Interlaced component images.
    Author:
    James Schmitz
